gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a48dda45c054f09bf119f983a93e99859350e3","tid":751274,"uid":32549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"早少少打去改堂好過喇"},{"pid":"c6a0f9b315f576981f76cdcce91f94489d302765","tid":751274,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問，我下年2月考駕院，正路考前3個月要上堂架嘛<br />\n咁我係around11月打去約師傅定係要再早d例如依家就打去約？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞定學牌，前3-4個月打去傾定時間就夠</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b2c091b7ed81520c6ccafe7e849be13e55d791","tid":751274,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ffe7627bf502c5d157f628d73aeda07c80617c","tid":751274,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"約時間盡早問，我跟開果位成日話無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976e5e6ac5647f4c2e57aacabd536ea61592d87c","tid":751274,"uid":159281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"試過有急事上唔到堂  打電話去中心冇人聽 <br />\n上網睇返星期日冇人接電話 但網上寫可以補行政費再按排上堂   <br />\n第二日打電話去問下要補幾多行政費可以補返上堂 佢答我唔係果日通知就冇得補返上堂 仲話電話唔通可以親身黎中心到搞 屌 我得閒去就上埋堂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌左幾句果職員都係支吾以對 話過左就冇得補堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過駕院有部份師傅係有禮貌教得唔錯 有d就寸寸貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ce2bf6368ed811ccfdf11e427fe05f1a269510","tid":751274,"uid":202106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"屌你 做乜刪ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" clas